text: Heoi, kei te takurua he ātaahuatanga rerekē kei reira, he nui ngā teihana e mūia ana e te huka i whānui rawa ai ngā mahi retireti hukapapa ki reira.
Ko ngā hōtērā ēnei i noho ai te hunga whai rawa o te rā, ā, he nui ngā wā ka kai pai ka pāti i te pō.
"He tino ātaahua ia, ā, he reo rōreka hoki tōna," hei tāna i roto i tētahi hopunga kōrero ki tētahi whare kōrero.
Whakakīia tōu whare ki tētahi kawhe mōmona i te ata, ki te tī kamomira whakatā i te pō.
E hangaia ana te nuinga o ngā pouaka whakaata kia reka ai ki te iwi whānui.
Kei te karapotia a Tākei e ngā moana ki ngā taha e toru: te Aegean Sea ki te uru, te Black Sea ki te raki, me te Mediterranean Sea ki te raki.
Ko ngā wāhi nui kei te raki e kōpā ana te noho a te tangata, engari anō ngā wāhi rō ngahere, kāore nei e tino pērā rawa.
Kāore i ngā Kuki Airani he tāone nui, engari 15 ōna motu. Ko ngā motu matua ko Rarotonga me Aitutaki.
Kei te hōkai 19,500 km₂ te rahi o te pāka, ā, kei te whakawehea ki ngā wāhi rauropi 14 rerekē, kei te tautīnei ia wāhi i ngā karerehe rerekē.
Ko te awa Amazon te awa nunui, roroa tuarua o te ao. Neke atu i te 8 reanga wai e pūritia ana e ia.
Kote whakatau a tētahi mātanga tahumaero nō te UN, a Danielle Lantagne, nā ngā kaipupuri rongopai te pakarutanga i para.
I mua i te taenga atu o ngā ope tauā, kua kore a Haiti i te pāngia e ngā raru e pā ana ki te tahumaero mai i te rautau 1800.
Ko te kitenga, ko te pūkenga kia kite rānei e whirinaki ana ki ngā whēkau rongo pūnaha kitenga, ki ngā karu rānei rānei.
Ko te hanganga o ēnei tioata e hāngai ana ki ērā ka kitea ki te mimi o ngā mōkai e pāngia ana ina ka whakatairitea mā te mātaitanga rārangi aho hihi pōkākā (infrared spectroscopy, FTIR).
Tirohia te tapanga mō ngā tohutohu āwhina tuatahi mō taua paihana motuhake.

I te tau 1994, i ara ake tēnei pakanga ki te hanganga o te Transnistria Republic ki te rāwhiti o Moldova nā rātou anō i whakapuaki, kei a rātou tō rātou ake kāwanatanga, pūnaha moni anō hoki, engari kāore i te whakamanatia e tētahi atu whenua he mema nō te Kotahitanga o Ngā Iwi o te Ao.
Nā ngā kaiwhakarite porotēhi i kī, āhua neke atu i te 100,000 ngā tāngata i tae ā kanohi atu ki ngā tāone nui o Tiamani pēnei i Berlin, i Cologne, i Hamburg, i Hanover.
Kei te noho haepapa ēnei kaiwhakahaere mō te tuku i ngā ratonga ā-kāwanatanga, ā-kōti anō hoki ki raro i te atikara 247 o te Pakistani Constitution.
Whai muri tata i te huakitanga mai o te riri, ka whakarite ai a Piritania tētahi aukatinga ope moana mō Tiamani.
I tū ngā porotēhi puta noa i te ao, he nui ngā hāmenetanga hara, ā, i heke katoa atu ngā rangatira o Iceland me Pakiston i ō rātou tūranga.

I te tīmatanga o te pakanga i haere rātou mā te moana, engari nā te hanga mai o te irirangi whakaata, ka mutu, he hāngai tika hoki, ka mate ngā waka whakatakere te ruku ki raro i te moana kia kore ai hoki e kitea.
I te heke haere o te reo Kariki, ka haukotia te Uru i ōna pakiaka wānanga, pūtaiao Kariki hoki.
Ko ngā katote hauwai i turaki iraoho me ngā irahiko (mai i te ngota hauwai kotahi te iraoho me te irahiko.
E whai whakaarotia ana te ngota hei tētahi o ngā mea pūtake ka hanga i ngā matū katoa.
E takahurihuri ana pēnei i ngā kāta tumaha mā runga i te puke. E whakawehe nei anō i te poka pū, ka tukuna ai ētahi o taua ngoi.
Ka whakaaro ake ētahi kaiaka he pai ake rātou ki tētahi taputapu ahakoa kāore he hua tika ka kitea.
Kua whara a Massa mō te roanga atu o tēnei tau 2009.
He iti noa te utu o te oma tawhiti, heoi, he nui ngā heitara mō ngā taputapu iti nei ka whakamahia mō tēnei mahi.
I te wā i taetae ngā waka i mua atu i a Alonso ki te whakakī i te hinu i raro i te waka haumaru, he neke whakamua ia i te katoa kia riro i a ia te wikitōria.
I riro i a Nadal ngā piro 88% i te whakataetae, ā, me te whiwhi i te 76 piro i te whiunga tuatahi.
Ko ngā manuhiri he iti te wā kua pai ake me i whai wāhi atu ki wāhi kē atu.
Hei āpiti, kia kamakama ka hau mai ngā pea me ngā atu kararehe puihi i te mea o ngā kakara, nā me ngana kia kauka e kawe e tunu rānei i ngā kai kakara, ā, me mā hoki te puni.
Mā te whakarite i mua e tau ai te hinengaro a te tangata hāereere he wāhi māna hei moe ina tae atu ki te wāhi rā.

Ko ngā huarahi whānui, ko ngā whare he karāhe te pakitara o mua, me ngā pokapū hokohoko hou e kōtingotingo ana i waenga i ngā tuanui papauku-whero, te mākete nō te rautau 18, me ngā mosque me ngā whare karakia tawhito, ahakoa kei te tāone nui te wairua ka nui ake te Mediterranean Europe i te Tākei o mua.
I ngā wā katoa, me whakarite e koe mā te waea tōtika atu ki te kamupene rererangi.
